ad_context:
12 bicycle ambassadors from 8 Asian countries, donning the newly designed GCC series riding gear, activating the GroupRide function on the Garmin Edge bike computer, and paired with the Vision Metron RS wheelset, embark on a 9-day circumnavigation journey around Taiwan!

Although initially impacted by the typhoon, the weather gradually cleared as they headed southeast, allowing them not only to fully savor the riding delights of the eastern coast but also to experience the finest hotel facilities of the Hotel Royal Group, along with the meticulously arranged "City Awakening Project," while immersing themselves in the charm of local morning culture!

來自亞洲8國的12位自行車大使，穿上全新設計的GCC系列騎乘裝備，啟動Garmin Edge自行車錶的GroupRide功能，搭配Vision Metron RS輪組，展開為期9天的台灣環島之旅！
雖然初期因颱風影響，但越往東南方向前進天氣逐漸轉晴，不只能盡情暢享東部海岸的騎行樂趣，還體驗到老爺酒店集團最棒的飯店設施，以及精心安排的"City Awakening Project"，同步感受在地清晨文化的魅力！

